  <h2>Sensitivity Analysis</h2>
  <p>Our base case uses {(growthRatePhase1 * 100).toFixed(0)}% growth and {(discountRate * 100).toFixed(0)}% discount rate. Here's how the intrinsic value changes under different scenarios.</p>

  <div class="table-wrap">
